                     <hi rend="largeCaps">EDWARD SIMPSON</hi> (39)</persName>, was indicted<rs id="t18690405-412-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18690405-412-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18690405-412-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="bankrupcy"></interp> for unlawfully obtaining on credit, within three months of his bankruptcy, certain goods of <persName id="t18690405-name-207" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18690405-name-207" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
