                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">and</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">WHITAKER</hi>. <hi rend="italic">conducted the Prosecution</hi>; <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. SERJHANT PARRY</hi>, <hi rend="italic">with</hi> 
